betterquesting:10.desc:8:
It is not just that nothing changed. It truly feels like everything I have done against my enemies yielded no results.
Sure, I did not expect my enemies to give up right away as my enemies were defeated, but I definitely did not expect this complete and utter lack of changes in their attitude.
This is puzzling. I thought I won the war, and yet defeating the rulers of my enemies changed nothing about their resolve.
Is this something I am not Fractallite enough to understand? Does this have anything to do with powers beyond me?
